	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" /><div class="quotetitle">FARID wrote:</div><div class="quotecontent">Please let me know about any kinds of mistakes :<br /></div>
<br />
<br />I looked over the mapper chips quick and everything there looks good. 
<br />
<br /> Just to make anyone aware that might be using this as a reference though:  FARID changed up the pins compared to the standard wiring.  It's all logically the same and will work fine, but things like which OR gate he chose to use for what signal are different.  So I wouldn't use it as an exact reference for standard UNROM boards.

		

		</td>
	</tr>
	</table>


